22:25.000 --> 22:36.000
and that that is the value of becoming aware of that, which, you know, if there were some greater understanding of it in our society,

22:36.000 --> 22:48.000
perhaps there would be less fear of one's own death, and less engagement in exhaustive health interventions right at the end of life,

