26:15.000 --> 26:22.000
until the last two or three hundred years, in which people were confident of some kind of personal immortality,

26:22.000 --> 26:34.000
even if the, let's say from Christianity, we have the West, very invested in the idea of personal immortality to the extent that

26:34.000 --> 26:37.000
