26:45.000 --> 26:51.000
that you're eternal if you think about God that you participate in his eternity,

26:51.000 --> 26:55.000
and that it's sort of an intellectual eternity, and that's something that Spinoza picks up on later.

26:55.000 --> 27:01.000
