29:51.000 --> 29:59.000
No, you're right. There's overreach there, and I think Max Tegmark, who's a colleague, I like him and know him well,

29:59.000 --> 30:08.000
he espouses the layers of reality and awareness and the fundamental, you know, Pythagorean idea of a mathematical universe,

30:08.000 --> 30:13.000
and it's an aesthetic. I mean, it's a pure aesthetic, and as an aesthetic, I agree.

30:13.000 --> 30:17.000
