So questions line up and state your name and please keep it in the form of a brief question.

01:24:17.000 --> 01:24:21.000
Yeah, for people, for myself and people I know, there isn't so much a fear of dying.

01:24:21.000 --> 01:24:25.000
It's the process of dying, the pain and suffering of dying.

01:24:25.000 --> 01:24:32.000
And I never understood the fear of dying because if you're religious, you're looking for something better for afterwards.

01:24:32.000 --> 01:24:37.000
And if you're not religious, it's all over. So where does the fear and anxiety come in?

01:24:37.000 --> 01:24:44.000
