01:24:44.000 --> 01:24:48.000
which is nothing, but to fear, to lose what you want to keep.

01:24:48.000 --> 01:24:54.000
That is to say, you have fear insofar as you conceive of death as the extinction of the possibility of experience,

01:24:54.000 --> 01:24:59.000
and you have an investment in going on, in continuing to have the possibility of experience.

01:24:59.000 --> 01:25:02.000
That's regret, not fear, isn't it?

01:25:02.000 --> 01:25:05.000
